{"tid":438833,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"排兵佈陣《雄據三國》 FAQ ！免課金速刷全橙隊！","createTime":"2017-10-17T09:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T07:32:41.000Z","uid":38794,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8cc1afb5458dc89bd53d0ebb18e7c31bf5a77b","tid":438833,"uid":38794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"Q：《雄據三國》是一套怎樣的遊戲？<br />\nA：一套三國策略遊戲，玩的是將士配合組隊以及 24 小時爭領土國戰。<br />\n<br />\niOS 下載：<a href=\"http://quickdownload.pro/sango6ios\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fquickdownload.pro%2Fsango6ios&d=0Rz6KV7ikgSXxF%2BtUSPczgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=43ace3df\" target=\"_blank\">http://quickdownload.pro/sango6ios</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid 下載：<a href=\"http://quickdownload.pro/sango6android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fquickdownload.pro%2Fsango6android&d=0Rz6KV7ikgSXxF%2BtUSPczgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=18a4dff8\" target=\"_blank\">http://quickdownload.pro/sango6android</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://is4.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple128/v4/1a/3a/37/1a3a370e-5720-1efc-fc2f-c895ef2b4be3/source/520x293bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fis4.mzstatic.com%2Fimage%2Fthumb%2FPurple128%2Fv4%2F1a%2F3a%2F37%2F1a3a370e-5720-1efc-fc2f-c895ef2b4be3%2Fsource%2F520x293bb.jpg&h=76e537e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/175023_f167e0401eedee14a43f698540501d0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F175023_f167e0401eedee14a43f698540501d0e.jpg&h=20ba84fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：好玩在哪裡？<br />\nA：喜歡佈陣類遊戲的人會很喜歡！因為每個將士的技能也不同，例如有些打單將 300% 輸出，有些則打全體，有些可冰封對手 2 回合，甚至火燒對手，令對人全陣每回合失兵。因此將士配合是遊戲的關鍵！《雄據三國》玩的就是佈陣！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/174607_aa2b79df92892eadceda5e0f75a1a7c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F174607_aa2b79df92892eadceda5e0f75a1a7c9.jpg&h=f2c05826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：開始時加入那個國家？<br />\nA：開始時可讓你選加入的國家，如果選隨機可得到 200 元寶！作為初體驗，我認為隨機入國即可，日後想認真地玩才找有大神加入的國家吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/174718_9e3be64f7e889fe57f521b85d4e7581b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F174718_9e3be64f7e889fe57f521b85d4e7581b.jpg&h=11155ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：要刷首抽嗎？<br />\nA：首抽就不用！不過 10 連抽就值得刷！基本上，一次10連抽可出 1-2 名橙將，如果你有一些好用的橙將，會有點優勢！而刷一次 10 連抽，不用 30 分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/174627_81e6aafc04abe06efaa3a2e206f198b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F174627_81e6aafc04abe06efaa3a2e206f198b2.jpg&h=a59c61e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：開局時的將士是固定的嗎？<br />\nA：是固定的，關平、張梁、蔡文姬是第一隊的固定將士，之後第二隊固定將士是盧植及祝融。由於是劇情指定角色，所以不會有任何改變。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/174743_f6cf489b41d286959ce92811618064a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F174743_f6cf489b41d286959ce92811618064a0.jpg&h=c7c195f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：開局的將值得培育嗎？<br />\nA：如果想快一點刷首次１０連抽，又不想浪費資源，建議除了關平要稍為突破至 +3 外，其他只升裝備+20 及滿等級即可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ：如何快速升到 16 Level？<br />\nA：首先，如果以筆者的建議，將關平突破至 +3，全隊裝備 +20 及滿等，你應該可順利通過劇情的 15 等任務，之後要進入 16 等就只能打「世界」劇本，這裡我們要爭城上陣殺敵，先要殺 3 萬兵，其餘隨便打打城，志在參予就可拿經驗升上 16 等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/174956_43514360a509774f770460ca6f756dc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F174956_43514360a509774f770460ca6f756dc0.jpg&h=8ac96359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：首次１０連抽在何時？<br />\nA：當你升到 16 Level ，就差不多可以夠 2800 元寶來一次１０連抽。筆者這時有 2560 元寶，餘下就只要打幾次「逆轉三國」的任務，肯定夠 2800 元寶！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/174817_14eaa0b4396175c342f00271fe36d110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F174817_14eaa0b4396175c342f00271fe36d110.jpg&h=a0c63f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQ：哪些橙將是開局最好用呢？<br />\nA：首刷如果有以下一位，其實也可開局，主要也是一些能夠秒殺對人的角色！其實不難抽！<br />\n<br />\n太史慈：高輸出，無視閃避<br />\n顏良：高防高輸出<br />\n夏侯惇：秘殺最少血的對手<br />\n馬超：兵越少輸出越高<br />\n司馬懿：封後排 2 回，非常實用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/174937_faf518e5de8fd97b72f82ec314e57a2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F174937_faf518e5de8fd97b72f82ec314e57a2d.jpg&h=bcb1cf0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：第７天送橙將該選誰？<br />\nA：顏良、馬超、陸遜、司馬懿，基本上４位也有用，但如果要選，我會選司馬懿，因為能阻擋對手攻擊，其次是顏良，然後是馬超，最後是陸遜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/174538_b55439b91028cd857f90d7c38c0ff051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F174538_b55439b91028cd857f90d7c38c0ff051.jpg&h=f913c8b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：隊應該如何組？<br />\nA：將士分為３類，攻擊型、防守型及輔助型。陣型一般是一攻一守一輔助。例如顏良（守）、司馬懿（助）、夏侯惇（防）可成為一組。<br />\n<br />\nQ：升級主隊有什麼技巧？<br />\nA：「突破」是重點，因為 +5 突破才可令將士使用第2 技能。跟著筆者的指示玩，我們只將「關平」突破過，所以將他重置再將突破令取回，留給橙將使用。<br />\n<br />\nQ：秘密商店買什麼？<br />\nA：買一些主隊角色的碎片，盡快將全隊主隊突破至 +5。不建議買一些未有的將士碎片。<br />\n<br />\nQ：要快速升等級可以怎樣？<br />\nA：打劇本，打逆轉三國，解國任，升科技，儲 2800 元寶，立即 10 連抽，盡快突破。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/174507_4490867f01f5b21784af52f8e08c1ae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F174507_4490867f01f5b21784af52f8e08c1ae4.jpg&h=1dfd202e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"545534da72e1667f5ade3dfb7207473866ec967d","tid":438833,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:09:33.000Z","msg":"推下<br />\n幾鍾意呢類遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12790436ee38d9caa493285c3027dd93924d3198","tid":438833,"uid":38794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T02:15:00.000Z","msg":"今日開新服，可以留意"},{"pid":"f2c3b034e5b6ee7cc65b6e508e595d0250cd050f","tid":438833,"uid":6619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"等緊佢開新服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14a89319693f2c57f06997e935c8ef65d9c0f7c","tid":438833,"uid":132543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"玩緊，魏國好唔夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de8aa79d5f215d0809ef6d6611cbc7c6555a5c3","tid":438833,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩緊，魏國好唔夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好玩咩<br />\n我down左覺得畫面太鳩del左"},{"pid":"0c8a45afd7d7d04d2e3e937dc530d8ef11186019","tid":438833,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"09de18ebce4719cf548aa6ee33c47de0d1a60c44","tid":438833,"uid":6619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:07:58.000Z","msg":"幾鍾意玩呢類型game，之前係2服魏國玩過，俾兩邊夾到仆街，加上我又遲咗一日玩，索性等新服課金玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1467f9c7f3f219d9457da7b032d0ddc1da6ff750","tid":438833,"uid":132543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾鍾意玩呢類型game，之前係2服魏國玩過，俾兩邊夾到仆街，加上我又遲咗一日玩，索性等新服課金玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三服我入魏，都係被人夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2fe33fe7653dbd2b4de65274369dc156b88cec","tid":438833,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:06:26.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯, 但無乜人玩"},{"pid":"9c5cbdcab931ec0e713cfc0de387b10b5fe5f486","tid":438833,"uid":125166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T21:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7c0a3599e4dde8803526f68b5497f3c1120f6e","tid":438833,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"好玩"}]}